54/* logging for client-facing objects */
55#define nvif_printk(o,l,p,f,a...) do { \
56 struct nvkm_object *_object = (o); \
57 struct nvkm_client *_client = _object->client; \
58 if (_client->debug == NV_DBG_##l || _client->debug > NV_DBG_##l) \
59 printk(KERN_##p "nouveau: %s:%08x:%08x: "f, _client->name, \
60 _object->handle, _object->oclass, ##a); \
61} while(0)
62#define nvif_fatal(o,f,a...) nvif_printk((o), FATAL, CRIT, f, ##a)
63#define nvif_error(o,f,a...) nvif_printk((o), ERROR, ERR, f, ##a)
64#define nvif_debug(o,f,a...) nvif_printk((o), DEBUG, INFO, f, ##a)
65#define nvif_trace(o,f,a...) nvif_printk((o), TRACE, INFO, f, ##a)
66#define nvif_info(o,f,a...) nvif_printk((o), INFO, INFO, f, ##a)
67#define nvif_ioctl(o,f,a...) nvif_trace((o), "ioctl: "f, ##a)
68#endif
